{"tid":2049472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府與銀行簽署「派1萬元計劃」 涉21間銀行 6月底接受登記","createTime":"2020-06-03T13:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T15:58:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"40cf4a1a1b618d002204908d92803bda20912497","tid":2049472,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/finance/20200603/YB4ZJV6WAO7OOKQD2BEDV7E6E4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200603%2FYB4ZJV6WAO7OOKQD2BEDV7E6E4%2F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=474b39f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200603%2FYB4ZJV6WAO7OOKQD2BEDV7E6E4%2F&h=3fa1ce30\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/finance/20200603/YB4ZJV6WAO7OOKQD2BEDV7E6E4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aNz6xLMkDzuGN30oKa8YO2qvKTI=/802x451/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UWDM5EODFK36DT6RM6GPUHNDD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaNz6xLMkDzuGN30oKa8YO2qvKTI%3D%2F802x451%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUWDM5EODFK36DT6RM6GPUHNDD4.jpg&h=5fe65b07&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波表示，現金發放計劃的籌備工作已進入最後階段，預計6月底開始接受登記，7月開始發放款項。財政司在今年度《財政預算案》宣佈向每名年滿18歲的香港永久性居民發放1萬元，以鼓勵本地消費和紓緩市民的經濟壓力。"},{"pid":"174eb29620ec29068d4c1d691a05527b14800dde","tid":2049472,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"政府今日（3日）與21間銀行代表簽署現金發放計劃服務協議。<br />\n<br />\n簽署服務協議的21間銀行將為現金發放計劃提供電子登記平台，欲以個人銀行戶口直接收取款項的合資格市民，可透過有關銀行的網站或網上理財服務進行登記。這是最快收取款項的方法。市民亦可向有關銀行遞交書面登記表格。"},{"pid":"a0aa0743a4e4af306f74bda7b85fcdaa56388b30","tid":2049472,"uid":99978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:04:15.000Z","msg":